slots.bio:
@flotze has steadily built a strong presence in the region’s underground scene over the past few years. Starting from his homebase at the @goethebunker, he has been playing clubs across the area and shaping a sound that feels raw, intense and straight to the point.

His sets are driven by dark atmospheric elements, rolling rhythms and focused on maintaining flow rather than chasing peaks. The result is a consistent, forward-moving energy on the dancefloor.

As one of the Co-Founders of @deliriumessen, he is also closely involved in building and strengthening the local scene beyond the DJ booth and pushing the local underground electronic music to new standards.
